members.name: scan
members.comment: Scans a single node.

param: p - a parameter value passed to the visit method
return: the result value from the visit method

members.name: scan
members.comment: Scans a sequence of nodes.

param: p - a parameter value to be passed to the visit method for each node
return: the combined return value from the visit methods. The values are combined using the reduce method.

members.name: reduce
members.comment: Reduces two results into a combined result. The default implementation is to return the first parameter. The general contract of the method is that it may take any action whatsoever.

param: r1 - the first of the values to be combined
r2 - the second of the values to be combined
return: the result of combining the two parameters
